From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Mon, 20 Apr 2026 19:24:25 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat(synthesis): dynamic timeout scaling + early preflight
 estimation
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Synthesis agent timeouts now auto-scale with video count (300s + 60s per
video) instead of a fixed 1800s. Override via --synthesis-timeout CLI
flag or config.json synthesis_timeout key. Two estimation checkpoints
log timeout/input-size info: immediately after playlist fetch (early
warning) and before Stage 05 (precise fill ratio + truncation check).

Rebased on top of e3ed970 (β reflexion retry); retry call also uses the
computed β timeout.

https://claude.ai/code/session_01RxnSjdy7R88RZt5uMdjbBH
